        "content": "<p>when adding rust support for linux kernel 4.19x, we encountered some building problems of rust_minimal.ko. Does anyone <br>\nknow how to solve this building error <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/OG4DydTlHLCWCZJD94CRG1Me/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/OG4DydTlHLCWCZJD94CRG1Me/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/35136/OG4DydTlHLCWCZJD94CRG1Me/image.png\"></a></div>",
