    {
        "content": "<p>Are you trying to backport rust support? It looks like your .o makefile rules only ever expect C source files, you probably need to make it check for either .c or .rs and then do something different based on what is there</p>",
        "id": 431788195,
        "sender_full_name": "Trevor Gross",
        "timestamp": 1712506156
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>yes, im trying to backport to 4.19 kernel, i have added  .rs rules in Makefile.buid , but its seems that the newly added .rs rule for .o will not run. the build system still matches .c rules for .o to build. Im confused about how to let make gofor my rust rules. this is what my <a href=\"http://makefile.build\">makefile.build</a> looklike <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/XBmgPdWTniLzCTU-99-lCHhx/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/XBmgPdWTniLzCTU-99-lCHhx/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/35136/XBmgPdWTniLzCTU-99-lCHhx/image.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 431832689,
        "sender_full_name": "Catastro Wings",
        "timestamp": 1712539677
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Makefiles aren't fun... What does the C section look like? Latest has</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code>#<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Built</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">composite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">parts</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">obj</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">/%</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>: <span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">src</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">/%</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">recordmcount_source</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FORCE</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">call</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">if_changed_rule</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">cc_o_c</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">call</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">cmd</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">force_checksrc</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 432039983,
        "sender_full_name": "Trevor Gross",
        "timestamp": 1712600260
    },
